{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train, as I said earlier, it was just packed with, with, with, human beings, and, and-- virtually on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once we were in there, they shut the doors on us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And hysteria just broke loose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was just like being trapped and having nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can just tell you that, again, I'm talking from the perspective of a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The horror and the feeling was unimaginable to me to this day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people were just unable to breathe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were just unable-- they we were just, just, packed in on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I believe the journey took-- I thought it was forever-- but I guess from the Lodz to Auschwitz was about two days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I thought it was earlier, or less time, but I believe it was like two days or more, maybe three days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people were virtually defecating and relieving themselves on each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was just-- it was just something beyond description.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the sound of the, of the, of the tracks and the wheels and the whistle of the train are the things that are most memorable to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All we kept doing was just embracing each other And silently just mourning--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moaning and crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, my sister, and my dad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everyone else who still had their families were just in a silent-- after the very first few hours of realizing what was going on, it was just like some hysteria.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, basically, you sort of settle into a, a unimaginable silence and helplessness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you just deal with it to the next level.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- --As bad as you think things are, they're just the beginning of what was to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
